{
  "_comment": [
    "Croatian + English BM25 eval fixture for Task 15 (multi-language recall).",
    "",
    "Schema",
    "------",
    "docs[]:",
    "  id       - unique document identifier (used in query relevance labels)",
    "  lang     - ISO-639-1 language code ('hr' or 'en')",
    "  text     - document body (short note / sentence)",
    "",
    "queries[]:",
    "  id       - unique query identifier",
    "  lang     - query language ('hr' or 'en')",
    "  query    - search string (inflected form that DIFFERS from form in doc)",
    "  relevant - list of doc ids that should appear in the top-1 result",
    "",
    "Design principle: for the Croatian arm, the query uses an inflected surface",
    "form that is morphologically distinct from the form stored in the doc body.",
    "Only a Croatian stemmer / lemmatizer that reduces both forms to the same root",
    "will retrieve the correct document.  English tokenization (no Croatian-aware",
    "normalisation) leaves the forms as separate tokens and cannot link them.",
    "",
    "Croatian inflection pairs exercised (root -> doc form | query form):",
    "  lijecnik  -> lijecnika (genitive)  | lijecniku (dative)",
    "  termin    -> termina   (genitive)  | terminu   (dative)",
    "  pregled   -> pregleda  (genitive)  | pregledu  (dative)",
    "  nalaz     -> nalaza    (genitive)  | nalazu    (dative)",
    "  recept    -> recepta   (genitive)  | receptu   (dative)",
    "  bolnica   -> bolnici   (locative)  | bolnicu   (accusative)",
    "  pacijent  -> pacijenta (genitive)  | pacijentu (dative)",
    "  lijek     -> lijeka    (genitive)  | lijeku    (dative)",
    "  ordinacija-> ordinacije(genitive)  | ordinaciji(dative)",
    "  krvni     -> krvnog    (gen.sg.m)  | krvnom    (dat.sg.m)",
    "  tlak      -> tlaka     (genitive)  | tlaku     (dative)"
  ],
